  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/d51835906d0d607f2c42a905015c51a7.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/d51835906d0d607f2c42a905015c51a7.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a heartless killing machine bent on eradicating humans in <i>BUTCHER</i>, a relentless 2D shooter that pushes the boundaries of action and pixelated gore. In a dystopian future where humanity is on the brink of extinction, you become the ultimate killing machine, driven by an insatiable thirst for destruction. As you navigate this grim world, you’ll face bloodthirsty foes in fast-paced, ultra-violent combat that leaves no room for mercy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/298007f5692917dc02edf5c3ee808177.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/298007f5692917dc02edf5c3ee808177.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a beautifully crafted pixel art style that pays homage to classic games while delivering a modern twist. The atmospheric soundtrack enhances the tension as you blast through waves of enemies, using an arsenal of brutal weapons designed for maximum carnage. Master your skills with precise controls and a satisfying combat system that rewards quick reflexes and strategic thinking. Each encounter is an opportunity to showcase your prowess as you adapt your approach to survive in this unforgiving environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/fca4381bc243beaa19e43bfc2d4b992a.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/fca4381bc243beaa19e43bfc2d4b992a.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse diverse and challenging levels, each filled with unique environmental obstacles and menacing foes that will test your abilities. As you progress, discover hidden secrets and unlock new weapons, and upgrades to customize your killing machine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/8c206ba08b4cbbe983d983ecff5ebf3b.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/8c206ba08b4cbbe983d983ecff5ebf3b.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embrace the chaos? Step into the world of <i>BUTCHER</i> and show no mercy as you unleash destruction on everything that stands in your way.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/d51835906d0d607f2c42a905015c51a7.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/d51835906d0d607f2c42a905015c51a7.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a heartless killing machine bent on eradicating humans in <i>BUTCHER</i>, a relentless 2D shooter that pushes the boundaries of action and pixelated gore. In a dystopian future where humanity is on the brink of extinction, you become the ultimate killing machine, driven by an insatiable thirst for destruction. As you navigate this grim world, you’ll face bloodthirsty foes in fast-paced, ultra-violent combat that leaves no room for mercy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/298007f5692917dc02edf5c3ee808177.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/298007f5692917dc02edf5c3ee808177.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a beautifully crafted pixel art style that pays homage to classic games while delivering a modern twist. The atmospheric soundtrack enhances the tension as you blast through waves of enemies, using an arsenal of brutal weapons designed for maximum carnage. Master your skills with precise controls and a satisfying combat system that rewards quick reflexes and strategic thinking. Each encounter is an opportunity to showcase your prowess as you adapt your approach to survive in this unforgiving environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/fca4381bc243beaa19e43bfc2d4b992a.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/fca4381bc243beaa19e43bfc2d4b992a.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse diverse and challenging levels, each filled with unique environmental obstacles and menacing foes that will test your abilities. As you progress, discover hidden secrets and unlock new weapons, and upgrades to customize your killing machine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/8c206ba08b4cbbe983d983ecff5ebf3b.poster.avif?t=1768578161\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/8c206ba08b4cbbe983d983ecff5ebf3b.webm?t=1768578161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embrace the chaos? Step into the world of <i>BUTCHER</i> and show no mercy as you unleash destruction on everything that stands in your way.</p>",
